===Ranging cape===
If a player has 99 [[Ranged]], they will have access to a duplicate version of the shop, with the only difference being the addition of the [[Ranging cape]]. The stock of this shop is '''not''' shared with the regular shop.
{{StoreTableHead|sellmultiplier=1000|buymultiplier=500|delta=10|hidecaption=y|smw=No}}
{{StoreLine|name=Ranging cape|smwname=Ranging cape#Untrimmed|buy=N/A|stock=1|restock=1|gemw=no}}
{{StoreTableBottom}}
===Ranging cape(t)===
For players with 99 [[Ranged]] and at least one other [[Skill mastery|99]], they will access a second duplicate shop. Just like the previous, the stock of this shop is not shared with the others.
